{
  "stem": "9156.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I ran out and said, what kind of a God is that?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was very upset about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I sat shiva with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I cried.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that was the beginning of questioning an awful lot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And now come all this other intellectual stuff that I said before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then comes all the friends with whom we talk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Is this really-- why are there different religions?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why are they-- are they all believing in the same God?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I had a very close friend, who later also was killed by the Nazis, but her mother and she belonged to something that I had never even known that existed.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't belong to any religion, and I didn't know that that's possible.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were very good people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But oh, I cannot describe the debates we had, I, saying that well, Moses heard God, so it must be real.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she says, no, it was just the thunder.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, these kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we have to remember that there is a lot of struggle in that period.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I decided I would not go any more to the synagogue, especially not to high holy days, because people only went there to wear their good clothes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think about 16.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had my own group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was already a leader at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There are thousands of other things I could tell about, but my goodness, we will never get into anything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But to say I said I wouldn't go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father was shocked, said he would forbid me to ever leave the house again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then I said it didn't matter to me, and I was crying.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had really heavy fights.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then he did something that I think was very smart.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He sent me to-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
